      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried some acetaminophen earlier but it didnt really do much for the pain. i really need something that actually works so i can get some work done. are you sure ibuprofen is that bad? i only need like one or two pills, surely a small dose won't mess up my kidneys if i'm just taking it once in a while.",
